 Disqus PHP API 示例  body{ max-width: 640px; width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; overflow-x: hidden; } body  * { width: 100%; } body a{ color: #0095dd; }     本页共有  条评论
项目地址：https://github.com/fooleap/disqus-php-api
var disq = new iDisqus('comment', { forum: 'fooleap', site: 'http://blog.fooleap.org', api: 'http://api.fooleap.org/disqus', mode: 2, timeout: 3000, popular: document.getElementById('popular-posts'), init: true, }); disq.popular(); disq.count();

